{"type":"message","id":"3a1bd36a","parentId":"a6f29480","timestamp":"2026-02-19T18:51:25.851Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-02-19 20:51 GMT+2] OPERATION: IRON CORE PHASE 5 (ORJSON & CIRCUIT BREAKER).\n\n1.  **Roadmap Audit (`ROADMAP_V7.md`):**\n    *   *Check:* Phase 4 (Cognitive) = COMPLETE.\n    *   *Action:* Mark checkboxes [x]. Move to Phase 5.\n\n2.  **Iron Core Upgrade (Benjamin):**\n    *   *Refactor:* Edit `src/dmarket/api/client.py` (or wrapper).\n    *   *Action:* Replace `import json` with `import orjson as json`.\n    *   *Optimization:* Use `orjson.loads()` directly on bytes response if possible (Zero-Copy).\n\n3.  **Circuit Breaker (Lucas):**\n    *   *Create:* `src/utils/api_circuit_breaker.py`.\n    *   *Logic:* Decorator `@circuit_breaker`. If latency > 500ms for 3 calls -> State = OPEN (Stop Trading). Reset after 60s.\n\n4.  **Auto-Doc:**\n    *   Run `python scripts/auto_doc.py`.\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   Thinking Block.\n    *   Roadmap Status.\n    *   Orjson Implementation.\n    *   Circuit Breaker Snippet."}],"timestamp":1771527085849}}
