on.\n\n\n**Adapting File Transformations**\n\n\\n\\n\n\nMy current thinking centers on the code adjustments. Replacing the original JSON import in `src/dmarket/api/client.py` with `orjson` is underway, alongside changes to how responses are parsed. I'm also planning the new circuit breaker implementation in a dedicated file, with a time-based reset and a specific latency threshold for triggering the \"OPEN\" state. Finally, the automated documentation task will be run after the code modifications are complete.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit_1771527134594_65","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"import orjson as json","file_path":"src/dmarket/api/client.py","oldText":"from src.utils import json_utils as json"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":18680,"output":1300,"cacheRead":17223,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19980,"cost":{"input":0.03736,"output":0.015600000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0034446000000000004,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0564046}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771527119183}}
